msgctxt "Addon Summary"
msgid "Atari - Jaguar (Virtual Jaguar)"
msgstr "Atari - Jaguar (Virtual Jaguar)"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "Virtual Jaguar is an emulator for the Atari Jaguar video game console.[CR][CR]Based on code released by David Raingeard (Cal2) of what used to be Potato Emulation."
msgstr "Virtual Jaguar je emulátor herní konzole Atari Jaguar.[CR][CR]Vychází z kódu, který uvolnil David Raingeard (Cal2) z někdejšího Potato Emulation."

